title: Health and Welfare Act 2013 (No. 15 of 2013), hereby make the following
heading: 2. The Animal Health and Welfare (Rabies) Regulations 2020 (S.I. No. 20
text_raw:
2. The Animal Health and Welfare (Rabies) Regulations 2020 (S.I. No. 20 

of 2020) are revoked. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

02 March, 2020. 

MICHAEL CREED, 

Minister for Agriculture, Food and the Marine. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 6th March, 2020.
